	on must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no el
	evator. Stairs only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at
	 door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety There is
	 an overall 8 ticket limit per patron Mobile barcodes and ticket transfer 
